jWebFit Navigation Test

Test starting at a URL, link navigation, and checking page title.

!!!!Story:
Beginning at the application menu, selecting the choose color link should navigate to the color selection page.
 
!!!!Testing the story:
We'll use baseUrl to establich the application root, navigate to the main menu, press the link, and check that we have the expected page title.
 
!!!!Succesful run:

[run]

Testing this page: http://localhost:8081/menu

|net.sourceforge.jwebunit.fit.WebFixture|||
|baseUrl|http://localhost:8081||
|begin|menu||
|check|title|Menu Page|
|press|link|Choose your favorite color|
|check|title|Choose Color|